data.description: WATERFRONT!!! Enjoy watching nature from your front windows or sitting on your own private dock and waterfront deck. Very rare to find Fox River with year round access to fishing, boating, skating, skiing and snow mobiles. Highly sought after Prairie Grove and Prairie Ridge school district.  This spacious home features three bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with a wood burning fireplace. Newer eat-in kitchen with loads of storage and counter space. Second floor features cherry wood floors and a desirable laundry room.  The large yard features two sheds for storage, a covered front porch deck and a new fire pit. Home does require Flood Insurance.  Property has 2 separate PINS. Don't miss out on a great opportunity to live on the water in a wonderful neighborhood
